headline: Tata Elxsi and Qualcomm partner to accelerate software-defined vehicle development
summary: The core of this collaboration involves Tata Elxsi’s creation of virtual ECU platforms using Snapdragon VSoCs.

headline: Qualcomm (QCOM) Upgraded to Buy: Here's What You Should Know
summary: Qualcomm (QCOM) has been upgraded to a Zacks Rank #2 (Buy), reflecting growing optimism about the company's earnings prospects. This might drive the stock higher in the near term.
